= Changelog

== v2.0.0

* Dropped Rails 2 compatibility
* Renamed 'alt' attribute to 'label'

== v3.0.0

* Support multiple ORMs
* Removed dependency on ActiveSupport & ActiveRecord
* Introduce abstract module Settler::AbstractSetting, which defines an interface for each ORM
* Namespaced settler objects under module Settler
  * The AR Setting is now class is now Settler::ORM::Activerecord::Setting
  * Typecaster is now Settler::Typecaster
